attribution.changeMessage: Name on birth/baptism record of Hans on 29 August 1824

Hans uses Mogesdatter in his journal, censuses it is Mogensdatter, Baptism/Christening of her children it is Mortensdatter, when her children are confirmed she is Martensdatter.  I am unsure if we have the correct Swedish Baptism record.
Immigrated with Hans Dinesen and family.  According to Hans' Journal, during the trip she sickened due to lack of proper food and died in Saint Louis five days after reaching there.
